sequenceDiagram
    title W5500 System Boot Sequence

    participant CPU as CPU / app_main
    participant CTL as TaskW5500Ctl (W5500CommCtl)
    participant COMM as TaskW5500Comm
    participant SPI as SPI Driver
    participant W5500 as W5500 (Hardware)
    participant ISR as ISR (GPIO INT)

    Note over CPU:
    CPU ->> CPU: app_main()
    CPU ->> CPU: AppInit()
    
    Note right of CPU: Create Control Task
    CPU ->> CTL: xTaskCreate(W5500CommCtl)

    activate CTL
    CTL ->> CTL: RxedPacket_Init()
    Note right of CTL: Create RxedPacket_Lock Mutex
    
    CTL ->> CTL: W5500_Create()
    CTL ->> SPI: spi_bus_initialize + spi_bus_add_device
    CTL ->> W5500: GPIO SCS=1, RST=1
    CTL ->> ISR: gpio_isr_handler_add(INT, W5500_IsrHandler)
    CTL ->> CTL: W5500_InitLock()
    Note right of CTL: Create W5500_Lock Mutex

    CTL ->> CTL: W5500CommCtl_Init()
    
    Note over CTL, W5500: --- Phase A: Reset & Sanity Check ---
    CTL ->> SPI: Write MR (0x0000, Common) = 0x80
    SPI ->> W5500: [00 00] [04] [80]
    W5500 -->> SPI: Hardware Reset Ack
    
    CTL ->> SPI: Read VERSIONR (0x0039, Common)
    SPI ->> W5500: [00 39] [00]
    W5500 -->> SPI: Return 0x04 (W5500 Version)
    SPI -->> CTL: Confirm HW Supported

    Note over CTL, W5500: --- Phase B: Network Config ---
    CTL ->> SPI: Write GAR (Gateway), SUBR (Subnet), SIPR (IP), SHAR (MAC)
    SPI ->> W5500: Burst Write Common Regs

    Note over CTL, W5500: --- Phase C: Interrupt & Socket Setup ---
    CTL ->> SPI: Write IMR=0x81, INTLEVEL=0x03E8
    CTL ->> SPI: Clear Ghost IR/SIR (Read then Write back)
    CTL ->> SPI: Write Sn_IMR=0x14 (RECV & SEND_OK)
    CTL ->> SPI: Write Sn_MR=0x04 (MACRAW)
    CTL ->> SPI: Write Sn_CR=0x01 (OPEN)
    W5500 -->> SPI: Socket 0 Status -> SOCK_MACRAW
    CTL ->> SPI: Write SIMR=0x01, Sn_RXBUF_SIZE=0x08 (8KB)

    Note right of CTL: Create Communication Task
    CTL ->> COMM: xTaskCreate(W5500_TaskComm)
    CTL ->> CTL: Save W5500CommCtl_TaskHandler
    
    activate COMM
    Note over COMM: TaskW5500Comm Startup
    COMM ->> CTL: xTaskNotifyGive(W5500CommCtl_TaskHandler)
    CTL -->> COMM: Task Notified
    COMM ->> COMM: ulTaskNotifyTake(wait forever)
    deactivate COMM
    
    Note over CTL: Join forever loop
    CTL ->> CTL: ulTaskNotifyTake(pdMS_TO_TICKS(5000))
    deactivate CTL